name: PRETTYMUCH - Better Than The First Time ft. Reo Cragun

metadata.description:
Welcome to our second official drop on sound, "Better Than The First Time." As we grow into ourselves in life and in music, we can't forget to give the girls their flowers. This song is about falling in love with a girl and letting her know how much power her love has over us through all its ups and downs. 

We had the pleasure of working with our friend Reo Cragun who has been nothing but supportive since the beginning of our careers. His presence on this record elevated the song so much and we hope you all agree!
metadata.name: Better Than The First Time #1
metadata.title: Better Than The First Time
